import pandas as pd
import seaborn as sns
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import matplotlib.ticker as ticker

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    plt.figure(figsize=(6, 6))
    sns.histplot(data=data, x='delay', bins=20)
    plt.title('What is the distribution of flight delays?', wrap=True)
    if len(plt.xticks()[0]) > 20:
        plt.gca().xaxis.set_major_locator(ticker.MaxNLocator(20))
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)
chart.show()

import pandas as pd
import seaborn as sns
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import matplotlib.ticker as ticker

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    plt.figure(figsize=(6, 6))
    sns.boxplot(data=data, y='distance')
    plt.axhline(data['distance'].mean(), color='r', linestyle='--', label=f"Average Distance: {data['distance'].mean():.2f}")
    plt.legend()
    plt.title("What is the average distance of flights in the dataset?", wrap=True)
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)
chart.show()

import pandas as pd
import seaborn as sns
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import matplotlib.ticker as ticker

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    plt.figure(figsize=(6, 6))
    
    data['date'] = pd.to_datetime(data['date'], errors='ignore')
    
    airport_counts = data['origin'].value_counts().reset_index()
    airport_counts.columns = ['origin', 'count']
    
    chart = sns.barplot(x='origin', y='count', data=airport_counts)
    
    if len(plt.xticks()[0]) > 20:
        chart.xaxis.set_major_locator(ticker.MaxNLocator(20))
    
    plt.xticks(rotation=45)
    plt.title('Which airports have the highest number of flights?', wrap=True)
    
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)
chart.show()

import pandas as pd
import seaborn as sns
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import matplotlib.ticker as ticker

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['date'] = pd.to_datetime(data['date'], errors='ignore')
    data['count'] = 1
    data_grouped = data.groupby('date').sum().reset_index()
    
    plt.figure(figsize=(6, 6))
    sns.lineplot(x='date', y='count', data=data_grouped)
    plt.title('What is the distribution of flights over time?', wrap=True)
    
    ax = plt.gca()
    if len(plt.xticks()[0]) > 20:
        ax.xaxis.set_major_locator(ticker.MaxNLocator(20))
    plt.xticks(rotation=45)
    
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)
chart.show()
